Steve Stricker Ties Verplank for Second-Round Lead at PGA Championship

-- B y   E r i k   M a t u s z e w s k i
-- 
2011-08-12T21:40:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/steve-stricker-ties-verplank-for-second-round-lead-at-pga-championship.html
Steve Stricker  birdied the par-5
12th hole to tie Scott Verplank for the lead at 5-under-par
during the second round at the U.S.  PGA Championship .  It was the second birdie of the round for Stricker, who
entered the day with a two-shot lead and is 2-over through 12
holes. Verplank is 2-under through 11 holes today at Atlanta
Athletic Club in Johns Creek,  Georgia .  D.A. Points,  Adam Scott ,  Jason Dufner  and Brandt Jobe are
tied for third place at 4-under par.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Erik Matuszewski at 
 matuszewski@bloomberg.net  